Capricious and dazzling the composed nature of the temptress acts as a veneer to her slick and clever thinking. Armed with rouge lips and Escada Desire Me she imprisons men without iron and chains. Intrinsic to the magnetic woman this sensuous Eau De Parfum is a glorious addition to the Me-House series from the elegant house of Escada.

The top note acts as an ambrosial delight with juicy-sweet extracts of clementine followed by a heart that is redolent of sweet clean notes of miva orchid fresh floral peony and nectarous honeysuckle with a fruity tinge. Finally the base note teases nostalgia with the memory of sitting at your favourite cafe awaiting the beautiful indulgence. Take in the warmth of tiramisu that is drizzled with thick luscious extracts of chocolate over creamy and milky mascarpone and sensual hints of coffee. Like the layers of a sinful dessert the accords of this luxury perfume are weaved together to enfold you in a delectably satisfying aura. Following the trademark shape of the Me-House series the Escada logo is immortalized in the form of this flacon. Combining statement-making hues of brilliant ebony and molten gold the diamond shaped crown and the glowing flacon make a solid impression. Alluring and seductive this perfume leaves behind a trail of admirers - victims of desire.

Escada Absolutely Me Eau de Parfum - 75 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.3255

Intensely addictive and ultimately tender a single whiff of Absolutely Me leads you down the path of olfactory nirvana. From the celebrated house of Escada the fragrance is an incredible sumptuous blend of the most succulent and mouth watering elements that leaves your senses begging for more. The luxury scent symbolises the raw desirability of a woman alluring and spontaneous. The Eau de Parfum draws you into its alluring depths leaving you lost in the luscious depths making you beg for more of its intense freshness. She is a woman of today who walks barefoot prefers sweatshirts and old shorts to haute couture and eats ice cream straight out of the carton and still manages to look beautifully perfect and Escada honors her need to be just herself and embrace all that she is.

All three layers of the fragrance are extremely delicious to the point where you start giving in to your cravings and indulge yourself. Creamy opening notes with accords of fresh red raspberries soft red rose and spicy pink peppercorns remind you of rich creamy desserts denied in favor of figure. The heart notes are lavishly scrumptious with the accords of jasmine and wild hawthorn. Smooth and saucy rose macaron adds its divine flavor to the melee. Absolutely Me closes with musky accords and edible texture of vanilla which gives the dry down a very creamy sensuality. Escada Absolutely Me is presented in a flacon that draws inspiration from the symbol of infinity which signifies the undeniable draw of the woman it adorns. Let the smooth warmth of Absolutely Me wash over you as you assert your independence and sensuality.

She’s brazen and unapologetic with a sanguine temperament a closet-narcissist who also believes in the beauty of others. An intriguing scent crafted for someone who stands apart in a league of her own battling preconceived notions and charging ahead. Escada Incredible Me parallels her vivacious nature - brimming with ideas and pulsating with energy. Inspired by a delectable plate of Tiramisu this intoxicating Eau De Parfum is made for the enigmatic house of Escada.

This incomparable woman deserves to be showered in an enriching balm that tingles and excites. A range of hand-picked ingredients fuse together and form an ethereal scent - fit for the woman who transcends definition. This perfume opens with fruity and sweet extracts of clementine that moves into a floral heart of powder-sweet orchid and light fragrant peony. Finally the base note mingles the aroma of luscious and creamy tiramisu with entrancing hints of coffee and deliciously rich chocolate. As she dabs on a bit of this hypnotic luxury fragrance she sends the multitude of admirers into a fervour. For an impactful fragrance the ampoule it comes in has to be spectacular. The appealing structure resembles the shape of a horizontal 8 emblazoned in sleek black and polished silver with the Escada logo. The final touch to this beautiful structure is the stopper that looks like a sparkling black diamond. She’s a mystery she’s a paradox - she is incredible.
